data.description: This comfortable home has plenty of space both inside and out, it has all hard floors downstairs and comfortable carpets upstairs. The layout of the house is great, and it has some definition between rooms, with a living room, family room with a half bath, and dining room all surrounding the spacious kitchen. The upstairs has a hall bathroom and four generously sized bedrooms. The primary bedroom has an en-suite full bathroom, a walk in closet, and a private deck! The back yard is very spacious, it is fully fenced in with a six foot tall privacy fence and has a large deck.
